
Stage 1
 * implement split_page_at_cursor (if contains more than 2 tuples)
 * reimpement the insert_tuple_at_cursor using the split_page_at_cursor function
 * implement merge_pages_at_cursor (if space_occupied by the tuples in both the pages equals the page_size - header size)
 * implement page_cursor delete at cursor
 * provide support to seek to -> end of current page, end of current tuple
 * implement page_cursor prev direction support
 * write test_cases and pass them

STAGE 2
